fields.title: CFI Workspace: Your All-in-One Hub for Seamless Church Management
fields.subtitle: Streamline church operations, manage activities effortlessly, and stay connectedall in one powerful platform.
fields.body:
We are pleased to introduce the CFI Workspace, a centralized platform that integrates all CFI applications, including the CFI Database, CBA Online System, and any future applications. The CFI Workspace will introduce Single Sign-On (SSO), allowing users to access multiple applications using a single account.

With this change, users who already have a CFI Database account will not need to create a separate CBA account when enrolling in CBA, and vice versa. Additionally, to enhance security and protect user accounts from external threats, only users with a CFI Workspace ID will be able to access the CFI Workspace.

Below are some Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs) to help users understand this transition.  

### Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)

#### 1.	What is a CFI Workspace ID? 
A CFI Workspace ID is a professional email address under the cfi.church domain, assigned by the system administrator. It consists of a combination of your first name and surname or an initial and surname. Example:  

-	jdoe@cfi.church 
-	janedoe@cfi.church 

#### 2.	What happens to my password when this change takes effect?  
Your current password remains unchanged. If you do not remember your password, you can reset it by following the instructions on either the CFI Database or CBA websites.

#### 3.	Will CBA students have access to the CFI Database?  
No. Access will be based on authorization levels and the type of CFI Workspace ID assigned to the user.

#### 4.	Will this change affect or delete my existing user data?  
No. Your user data will remain intact and will not be affected by this transition.

#### 5.	When will this change take effect?  
The implementation is scheduled for Monday, March 3, 2025. Users will be notified once the change has been successfully implemented.

### Additional System Updates

Along with this transition, we will also be implementing updates on the CFI Database, including:  
-	Bug fixes on the Regular Expenditure form 
-	Users experience improvements

To ensure a smooth transition, a meeting will be scheduled to demonstrate and explain these changes in detail.

For any questions or concerns, please feel free to reach out.

fields.title: Introduction
fields.body:
# CFI Workspace Documentation

Welcome to the official documentation for CFI Workspace, the all-in-one platform designed to seamlessly integrate **CFI Database** and **Cornerstone Bible Academy**. Whether youre managing church operations, tracking attendance, handling finances, or engaging in Bible studies, **CFI Workspace** simplifies your workflow by unifying applications, automating processes, and keeping everything in sync.

# What is CFI Workspace?

CFI Workspace is a centralized ecosystem that connects and enhances CFI applications, enabling effortless management of church activities and Bible education. It provides a seamless experience across:
- **CFI Database**  A robust church management system that streamlines administrative tasks, financial tracking, and attendance monitoring.
- **Cornerstone Bible Academy**  An interactive learning platform offering structured courses to deepen faith and spiritual growth.

Designed for efficiency and ease of use, CFI Workspace ensures that all applications work together smoothly, eliminating redundancy and improving productivity for churches, leaders, and members alike.

This documentation will guide you through everything you need to know to get started, integrate applications, and make the most of CFI Workspace.

fields.title: Please pray for my health
fields.description: Please pray for my health. Ive been feeling very unwell and need urgent healing. The doctors are unsure of the cause, and I'm extremely worried. I need strength and peace during this time.

fields.title: Urgent Financial Breakthrough
fields.description: Please pray for me as I am facing serious financial struggles. Unexpected expenses have left me overwhelmed, and I need Gods provision and wisdom to manage my situation. I trust that He will make a way where there seems to be none.

fields.author: John Doe
fields.title: Prayer for Peace and Calm in Our Daily Lives
fields.description: Please pray for peace and calm in our daily routines, that we may find tranquility amidst the busyness and challenges of life. May we feel the presence of Gods peace in every moment, no matter how small or insignificant it may seem.

fields.title: Prayer Warriors - Healing Through Faith
fields.body:
Weekly prayer circle focused on interceding for community healing, health challenges, and personal restoration. 

No matter what youre going through, Gods love for you never changes. He sees you, He knows you, and He cares for you deeply. I have loved you with an everlasting love.  Jeremiah 31:3.

fields.title: Trust in Gods Timing
fields.body: Sometimes, waiting feels like the hardest part, but Gods timing is always perfect. Keep praying, keep trustingHe is never late!  The Lord is good to those who wait for Him.  Lamentations 3:25
